&gt;Replace the neuron-count proxy with Rethink Priorities&#x27; welfare-range estimates (Fischer et al.) and count invertebrates — shrimp, insects, and the ~10^19 soil animals. Under RP medians a chicken&#x27;s welfare range is a third of a human&#x27;s, not a fiftieth, and wild/soil invertebrates carry significant aggregate (nematode) weight, so invertebrate work dominates. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 nature_intrinsic_value → 4 climate_tipping_points → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 7 animals_matter_a_lot" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylWGtv2zgW%2FSsXwXbWzvghy293s0CaONOiSRskKYJBXbi0RNucSKSWpOK6nfa37yUp2XKsTg3kSyJL5Lnnvi%2F57Sikc5JG%2BkyE9Gh01GzCyckJ3EnCOGgBgSRf1%2Fiw4jBJfa%2FVgZWQUfjI6ApWrak%2FbU870%2B60DxWlRQL9qtk%2B4QhzqlQaJ5oJDsES0UbgQUKkCJaMRAasNfShBXMip2RF1tNlGhOu8g8%2BEM5iEqmpEjFdLYnOv7SBE51KOmVcS8YVC6aPJEpp%2Fr0DQYQ7NZ1qliSML6aJwKUb5C7MU7vfCZziUk3ldMX0choyFYiUa9yVL%2B9viGQLyTQS2mo4JsESyFZNpoDA9Vov8XnOIgpowu1n1QRt1CBhqGogKdqdcapASAsmaR2tQ2KKMpjC93pJneH%2BrZAxDyzGSwhEnAhlCG4W4F4eUkTEV0xZNKUJD0kkOIUYHRs14PPGb%2BPHz4aq2U6%2FJDTQuNFZUMwtwtbFDQv2iioNs3QNqRFjNipaVGwEt0vJ4gTuaYTupHAtxV%2BI63b%2FMX43vjm9G5%2FDbA0LyqlE3zSSdR5PNGR6x0zH%2BLEGXGhHxlgSkSzWBx5QqY3KsZAYRRuLKbfWmYMkScSoasDtOm5EYsGFRAdWviXdGiTD7veqxbLeGnov4OzNS7tyRjVxbxMpZmTGIqaRyEwYtUOTDB%2B9GrQ%2BNeCCBFqgTNTVQeGCxPiA6xooAdQEhpAL9Nz44%2Br89PLP5r8%2BwYxGYoXxbvZaD9Mv%2BBytcTtio1UtFsoO00A7X6D3KMYoqu9i%2Fh59ur6m8jVa1xj6ZF9FTLOG17KKjsD%2FXgVAUMuhTv%2BXMnQ0soQE%2FbjMQFCitlEwQqPzekzkA9VIjilN0d51FxtNuL%2B7hrnAfWgaTVDTQPBHdIezjRUBlUAKpeoBYj%2Fge%2FS4pI8UZYZA%2BSOTgsconkT1WDxS8wiKBJLNWUDRK4iOoXbn0vZMzDBY5hgcpVrmKnYyFbOkR1L1fB%2Bm4UY30FIkLMCYcUJGcBqTr7giZHRGggfn%2BKxiAI0sOetMsjEUFgFh8kBthGH5SSVBI0149urcOeguEP5PveP5GXd83vGQdYs%2Be%2B%2BjLGfZEbxCtirC9xjxaDgMSVRR2fgIiJyhBpUfvcaA1ttgA01X4Xe4fvMWuWGpsBWCcxpB5a3QX5uX6A3kwnnznvKv8KM1fGGc5HudYQ2QaT3flbsWvZIZ5dpU0SvsFMxkl%2Fxnr%2FQytbK9dVuCgcS4FX1NbLmc0bXgIahYCL2EkMRkgUlRuRHBg9JyknrevBe79CMS8%2FklnM