l get-off point, not combined with astronomical-stakes longtermism (no_discounting_future_humans), where x-risk dominates and the meat bookkeeping is moot. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 nature_intrinsic_value → 4 climate_tipping_points → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 7 animals_matter_a_lot → 8 suffering_focused → 9 meat_eater_problem" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJytWW1z0zoW%2FitnmGU3gSZ1nPey3ZnSlwtDgU4py9yhTFBsJdHWtryS3RC48Nv3kWQnTpve5k72Ax1jS895zvuR8uNJyCcsj7JjGfInB0%2F29%2Bnw8JCuFBMJZZICxb4v8DBP6Dr3vVaH5lJF4a3gc5q3Rv6oPeqMuqP%2BaDAaUk1nMqVh3UBcJ4A60jqP00zIhIIZEA%2FIo5QpGcwEiwxga%2BhTiyZMjdicLUazPGaJLj%2F4xBIRs0iPtIz5fMay8kubEpblio9EkimRaBGMblmU8%2FJ7h4IIOzM%2BykSaimQ6SiWWLpG7NMntfidwhKUZV6O5yGajUOhA5kmGXeXy%2FpJIsZCNIrkkMyCdTyZcGTETGeSah%2BWnIcWcZSP8w6ZUyXHEY2uYUxbMiK2sIzQxulhkMzxPRMQJ1l991vuUGe1ZGOo9UhwuEwnXJJUFU7wBo7KYQ4rQeJ%2FNuLP3PzQUTQKL8YICGadSG72WC7A3CTkQ8Upoi6YzloQskgmnGDERNenr0uWnt18NVbOdf0t5kGGjM7ycWIRVdDQt2EuuMxrnC8qNGLNR86piB%2FRhpkSc0iceIQo4XSj5H%2BC63b%2Bdvju9PLo6PaHxgqY84QqGbKaLMhR5KLI1Mz3Dxz1K4BtLxlgSSBbrYxJwlRmVY6kQfEuLabfWmYOlaSS4btKHRdyM5DSRCn6v%2FUi7e5QOuz%2FrFst6a%2Bg9pePXL%2BzKMc%2BYe2uczMYiEhmIjKVROzR59Nnbo9aXJp2xIJOQCV0dFBakxgdJtkdaEjeBIdUUnjv9PD85Ov99%2F29faMwjOUeamL3Ww%2FwbnqMFtgMbVrVYkB3mQeZ8wU3oJRrqTyKZY9cMjj8pYpsO7yuI3Gx6A6umeRz8rBPZ4AImdJhzMZ0BG5msEM8mimbM5BbXmmpXMmZa3Lygf0Mh8833fA%2FGWmbGhRKgni02S241W4XgXrNbCObfMsUqYtkt%2FGegoTNPEEZL7IfFuyrxCeG8uODqFQLLxNhDypcc%2FIKBNX%2BD%2FzcXiHE4iFKE8KwAgbEzmwAHiLekETN1wzOQFhrsAt5wabFPn64uaCKxD1GRMTg5kInRxIWFFUG1QEmtGwGwb%2FAewa74LYfMkHhyK5RMYohnUSOWt9w8kmaBEhMRcCgJdGTZlSt0x3KMPJmIB1xcqtgpVCzKJEg1yn0w9VI3ypRMRYB0cUIO6Chm37EiFHzMghsX80WNJR5ZcjaO2dJQKJvSlAC9FIaCnSsGI10nxasT56CrQPoPesfzl7HprXnIuiU7fu9zFyPGJS%2FBVkd4j2SH4UzgBVLb1AiYGkOD2q9ec8AbbbI5ltXpOV28fgNuqJK2OCYJj6j2Rmbf98%2FhDXBJkv1PPPlOv1rDp8ZJvtcZ7hGYNspdpWvhlcIoF6bvvEV%2FFaawqD%2F3Sq9Qq9jbsE2LWIyt8DWznWLMFzIJScdSZjMKWcymqAe1Sxnc6Exd55436cWu8jCFUvaCjlSMLxIOehu8YQtCmD