oblem + net_negative_animal_lives + soil_animals&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Grilo&#x27;s soil-animal accounting: ~10^19 soil nematodes, mites and springtails dominate the welfare effects of almost anything. Global-health charities raise food demand and cropland (~137 m^2-yr/$ for GiveWell top charities, ~1.11 kQALY/$ of soil-animal welfare change); with soil lives net-negative, the arithmetic makes GiveWell&#x27;s top charities net-harmful. Only enters once invertebrates already count, so it requires animals_matter_a_lot; like the meat-eater problem it is a near-term get-off point, not combined with astronomical-stakes longtermism, where the cropland bookkeeping is moot. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 nature_intrinsic_value → 4 climate_tipping_points → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 7 animals_matter_a_lot → 8 suffering_focused → 9 meat_eater_problem → 10 net_negative_animal_lives → 18 soil_animals" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJytWWtz2zYW%2FSt3MttdKbVkUm85651xYrvNxEk9jruZTpxRIBKSsCYJLkBaUdL0t%2B8BQEqULdfsaD%2FEw5DEuec%2BcQh9exbyGcuj7JUM%2BbOjZ4eHdHx8TNeKiYQySYFiX1e4WCZ0k3c8v0dLqaLwTvAlLf1JZ9Kd9Cb9yXAymownvjfxR9TQmUzJHzUN0k0CxBOt8zjNhEwoWAD4iDxKmZLBQrDI4PrjDvk0Y2rClmw1WeQxS3T5oEMsETGL9ETLmC8XLCufdClhWa74RCSZEokWweSORTkvn%2FcoiLAy45NMpKlI5pNU4tU1cp9muV3vDE7wasbVZCmyxSQUOpB5kmFV%2BfpwTaR4kU0iuSYzIp3PZlwZMzMZ5JqH5aMxxZxlE%2FzDolTJacTjtdseJTybJHzOMnHHJ87EJML1mieCqqWIimfaxvSMBQtim8AKTYwuV9kC1zMRcUL%2BNo%2F1IWUmcCwM9QEpjqSLBAaksmCKt5APFnMQFBr3swV3qfqHRoySwGK8oEDGqdQmJOsXsDYJORBxSzhqOmNJyCKZcIpRVVGbPq%2BL5uzus6FqlvMvKQ8yLHQ5kzOLsKmvtgV7yXVG03xFuTFjFmpedeyI3i%2BUiFP6wCMUEKdLJf8DXLf6p7N3Z1cn12enNF3RnCdcIQftdFUWMw9FthWm53h4QAnSasmYSALJYv2aBFxlxuVYKtTtOmLavevCwdI0Ely36f0qbkdynkiFnDW%2Bpf0DSsf9702LZbM19n6gV69f2DenPGPurqkPNhWRyEBkKo3boenEj94B%2BZ%2FadM6CTMImfHVQeCE1OUiyA5QJcVMYUs2RubOPy9OTi98O%2F%2FaJpjySS3SYWWszzL%2FgOlphObARVYsF22EeZC4X3FRtouH%2BLJI5Vi2Q%2BNOiLej4oYNo67Y3sm6ay9H3JpEtLmDChyUX8wWwMQQUWsF