omical-stakes longtermism, where the cropland bookkeeping is moot. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 nature_intrinsic_value → 4 climate_tipping_points → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 7 animals_matter_a_lot → 8 suffering_focused → 10 net_negative_animal_lives → 18 soil_animals" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJytWWtz2zYW%2FSt3MttdKbVkUm85651xYrvNxEk9jruZTpxRIBKSsCYJLkBaUdL0t%2B8BQEqULdfsaL94aJI499wnDqFvz0I%2BY3mUvZIhf3b07PCQjo%2BP6VoxkVAmKVDs6woXy4Ru8o7n92gpVRTeCb6kpT%2FpTLqT3qQ%2FGU5GE9%2Bb%2BCNq6Eym5I%2BaBucmAd6J1nmcZkImFCwAe0QepUzJYCFYZFD9cYd8mjE1YUu2mizymCW6fNAhloiYRXqiZcyXC5aVT7qUsCxXfCKSTIlEi2Byx6Kcl897FERYmfFJJtJUJPNJKvHqGrlPs9yudwYneDXjarIU2WISCh3IPMmwqnx9uCZSvMgmkVyTGZHOZzOujJmZDHLNw7VrHiU8myR8zjJxxycOZhLhes0FgdNSRMUzbeN2xoIFsU3whCZGl6tsgeuZiDghQ5vH%2BpAyExwWhvqAFEdaRQIDUlkwxVuIOYs5mAuN%2B9mCu3T8QyMOSWAxXlAg41Rq4%2Fb6BaxNQg5E3BKOms5YErJIJpxi1E3Ups%2Frsji7%2B2yomuX8S8qDDAtdXuTMImwqqG3BXnKd0TRfUW7MmIWaVx07ovcLJeKUPvAIRcLpUsn%2FANet%2Funs3dnVyfXZKU1XNOcJV8h4O12V5cpDkW2F6TkeHlCC1FkyJpJAsli%2FJgFXmXE5lgq1uY6Ydu%2B6cLA0jQTXbXq%2FituRnCdSIWeNb2n%2FgNJx%2F3vTYtlsjb0f6NXrF%2FbNKc%2BYu5sqOWVTEYkMRKbSuB2aXvvoHZD%2FqU3nLMgkbMJXB4UXUpODJDtAmRA3hSHVHJk7%2B7g8Pbn47fBvn2jKI7lEF5m1NsP8C66jFZYDG1G1WLAd5kHmcoHscVQ%2B3J9FMseqBRJ%2FWpQ%2BHT90EK3b9kbWTXM5%2Bt4kssUFTPiw5GK%2BADYaXXFmm2fBTOtxralxLWOmxe0L%2BjccMs86XsdDsNaNc6kEqGer3Zb9tl8YHrT7hWH%2BJVOsYpbdIX8GGj7zBGW0xn7cvBsiH1DOq0uufkZhmRp7zPmSQ6dgYMPf4v%2FNBWocCaIUJbwoQBDszDbAEeotacVM3fIMpIUGu4C3XFsc0ofrS5pJrENVZAxJDmRiPHFlYU1QI1BS61YA7FvcR7ErfsdhMySe3AklkxjmWdSK5R03l6RZoMRMBBxOAh1ddu3m4Cs5RZ%2FMxCMpLl3sFS4WUxSkWuU6hHrtG2VKpiJAuzgjR3QSs694IxR8yoJbV%2FPFCCYeWXK2jtk6UBh50owAvTaGeZ4rhiDdJMWtU5eg60B2Hs2O11nXpreVIZuW7NUvHe5qxKTkJdjqCPfR7AicKbxAatsaAVNTeND4Y9Ae8VaXbI9lTfqRLl%2B%2FATdMSTsck4RH1Hgjs6%2BHF8gGuCTJ4QeefKU%2F%2FPEPJkkdrzc%2BIDBtlavK1CIrRVAuzbb0FnuwMINF%2FXlWBoVbxdqW3dOIxViKXDO7U0z5SiYh6VjKbEEhi9kc86BxJYNbnamb3PNmg9hNHqYwyl7QiYrxRCJBb4M3bEUoU4apjhbpIBg6YCHXp