rg is charged an additive penalty — farmed-animal life-years caused per human DALY, times the suffering per factory-farmed life-year, times the animal&#x27;s welfare range. Under a heavy animal welfare range the penalty can exceed the human benefit, so saving human lives looks net-harmful. Only bites once animals count, so it requires animals_somewhat; and it is a near-term human-vs-animal get-off point, not combined with astronomical-stakes longtermism (no_discounting_future_humans), where x-risk dominates and the meat bookkeeping is moot. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 nature_intrinsic_value → 4 climate_tipping_points → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 7 animals_matter_a_lot → 9 meat_eater_problem" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylWWtv2zgW%2FSsXwXbXzvghyW93s0CaONOiSRskGQSDunBpiba5kUgtKcV1O%2B1v30tSsuVYuxXgD21ViTz33Pcl%2Ff0koAuShsmFCOjJ%2BKTdhrOzM3iQhHFIBPiSfNvgw5rDNPUctwtrIcPgmdE1rN2ZN%2BvMurPebDAbQU0lIoZRXQNMOQKdK5VGccIEB3%2BFeGNwICZS%2BCtGQg3njjxwYUHkjKzJZrZKI8JV%2FsEDwllEQjVTIqLrFUnyLx3gJEklnTGeSMYV82fPJExp%2Fr0Lfog7EzpLWBwzvpzFApdukXuwSM1%2BK3CGSxMqZ2uWrGYBU75IeYK78uWDLZFsIZmFYktmBBElyQz%2F4JdYinlII6P9hPgrIDsTMAUEbjfJCp8XLKSABt59Vm1ItIokCFQDJEWvME4VCGnAJG2i5UhEUQpT%2BD5ZUWvUfyjUhvsG4zX4IoqF0uS3C3AvDygi4iumDJpKCA9IKDiFCN0etuDL1quT5y%2Baqt5Ov8bUT3Cjta5YGIRdALQM2BuqEpinG0i1GL1R0aJiY7hfSRbF8EhDdDWFWyn%2Bjbh29%2B%2BTD5O784fJJcw3sKScSjRkK97k0UYDluyZ6RQ%2FNoCjAwwZbUlEMlh%2FcJ%2FKRKscCYkRtrWYsmutOUgch4yqFtxvolYollxIdG7te9xrQDzq%2FagbLOOtkfMKLt69NivnNCH2rXYymbOQJUhkLrTagU6VT04D3M8tuCJ%2BIlAm6mqhcEGsfcCTBigBVAeGkEv03OTT%2BvL8%2Bs%2F23z7DnIZijbmg9xoP06%2F4HG5wO2KjVQ0Wyg5SP7G%2BoDr0uEL1bT48ok83t1S%2BRetqQ58dqogp2HJco%2BgYvB91AAQ1HJr0PylDRyNLiNGPqwwEJSYmCsZodN6MiHyiCZJjKqFo76aNjTY8PtzCQuA%2BNE1CUFNf8Gd0h7WNEQE1Xwqlmj5iP%2BF79LikzxRlBkD5M5OCRyiehM1IPFP9CIr4ki2YT9EriI6h9mBT%2BkLMMVgWGBylWuYqdjMVs4KApJr5PkzDrW6QSBEzH2PGChnDeUS%2B4YqA0Tnxn6zjs2oCNDTkjDPJ1lBYIITOA7UVhqUplQSNNOXZq0vroAdfeP%2FTO46XccfnPQ8ZtyQ