;s soil-animal accounting: ~10^19 soil nematodes, mites and springtails dominate the welfare effects of almost anything. Global-health charities raise food demand and cropland (~137 m^2-yr/$ for GiveWell top charities, ~1.11 kQALY/$ of soil-animal welfare change); with soil lives net-negative, the arithmetic makes GiveWell&#x27;s top charities net-harmful. Only enters once invertebrates already count, so it requires animals_matter_a_lot; like the meat-eater problem it is a near-term get-off point, not combined with astronomical-stakes longtermism, where the cropland bookkeeping is moot. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 nature_intrinsic_value → 4 climate_tipping_points → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 7 animals_matter_a_lot → 9 meat_eater_problem → 10 net_negative_animal_lives → 18 soil_animals" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylWftz0zoW%2FlfOdJbdpDcP23mH7c6UPi4MLXRK7zB3KGMUW0m0tSWvJDcELvzteyTZidN4l8z0B8DY0ne%2B8z5Svh%2FFdE7yRJ%2BJmB5Nj7pdODk5gTtJGActIJLk2xofVhzu88Dz%2B7ASMokfGV3Byg%2BDsBf2w0E4Cieh74X%2BGBpKiwz8cdPg3HPEO1UqTzPNBIdoibBT8CAjUkRLRhKD6k8C8GFOZEhWZB0u85RwVX4IgHCWkkSFSqR0tSS6%2FNIDTnQuaci4lowrFoWPJMlp%2Bb0PUYI7NQ01yzLGF2EmcOkGeQDz3O53AkNcqqkMV0wvw5ipSORc465y%2BWhDpFhIwkRsyEwgpUSH%2BAe%2FZFLMEppudPOAUx1yuiCaPdLQ4YQJPm%2FIoOWUYEnxTVnDXZBoCWRrPaaAwM1aL%2FF5zhIK6KLtZ9UFbaxD4li1QFL0K%2BMoQEgLJmkbjU5SigSZwvd6SZ0%2F%2FqHQEDyyGC8hEmkmlNF7swD38pgiIr5ijprShMckEZxCioGTdODLJi4uHr8YqmY7%2FZrRSONG5xgxtwjbEOpYsFdUaZjla8iNGLNR0apiU%2FiwlCzN4CNNMEoo3Ejxb8R1u3%2B%2FeHdxe3p3cQ6zNSwopxJ90MnWZbzSmOkdMx3jxxZw9J0lYyyJSBbrDx5RqY3KqZAYnBuLKbfWmYNkWcKo6sCHddpJxIILiT5rfM8GLcgmgx9Ni2W9NfFewNmbl3bljGri3pr4IDOWMI1EZsKoHZtk%2B%2BS1wP%2FcgUsSaYEyUVcHhQsy4wOuWxgmQE1gCLlAz118Wp2fXv3Z%2FdtnmNFErDCNzF7rYfoVn5M1bkdstKrFQtlxHmnnC2qilitU36XSR%2FTp%2BobK12hdY%2BiTfRUxezuebxWdQvCjCYCglkOb%2Fidn6GhkCRn6cVmAoERto2CKRuftlMgHqpEcU5qivdsuNrrw8e4G5gL3oWk0QU0jwR%2FRHc42VgQ0IimUakeI%2FYDv0eOSPlKUGQPlj0wKnqJ4krRT8UjNIygSSTZnEUWvIDqG2p2