 lives-eq/$1k · 97% best&lt;br&gt;   runner-up Rainforest Trust · 3%&lt;br&gt;(Brian Tomasik, David Pearce)" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + animals_somewhat + nature_intrinsic_value + climate_tipping_points + future_humans_matter_with_discounting + suffering_focused&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Asymmetry: averting intense suffering takes priority over creating happiness. Factory farming, malaria and the worst wild-animal conditions weigh up; speculative future-flourishing bets weigh down. Arises most naturally from taking animal suffering seriously, so it requires animals_somewhat. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 nature_intrinsic_value → 4 climate_tipping_points → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 8 suffering_focused" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylWW1T2zoW%2FitnmO1u0kuC47zTZWcoL7ed0pYBup07pZMqtpJosS2vZJOmve1v30eSnTgQbsPyhTG29JznvB8p33dCPmF5lB3JkO%2Fs7%2Bzt0cHBAV0pJhLKJAWKfVvgYZ7Qde57rQ7NpYrCW8HnNG%2BN%2FFF71Bl1RwOq6UymNKib7dcJYA61zuM0EzKhYAa0ffIoZUoGM8EiA9Ya%2BtSiCVMjNmeL0SyPWaLLDz6xRMQs0iMtYz6fsaz80qaEZbniI5FkSiRaBKNbFuW8%2FN6hIMLOjI8ykaYimY5SiaVL5C5NcrvfCRxhacbVaC6y2SgUOpB5kmFXuXxAOp9MuDJAExnkmodWvRMWzIitdBSaGJ0vshmeJyLiBPutPus9yowOLAz1LikOo4uEa5LKginegGlYzMFEaLzPZtxZ7R8adJPAYrygQMap1IbdcgH2JiEHIl4JbdF0xpKQRTLhFMOrUZO%2BLJ12cvvFUDXb%2BdeUBxk2OvPJiUVY%2BbdpwV5yndE4X1BuxJiNmlcV26crYL0ytuR0xtk0527j7yfvTi4Or06OabygKU%2B4gk%2Ba6aKMIx6KbM1Cz%2FFxlxKZOR7GiECyWB%2BSgKvMaBtLhehZGku7tc4SLE0jwXWTLhdxM5LTRCpEUO172t2ldNj9UbdY1lFD7xkdvX5hV455xtzbVMkxG4tIZCAylkbj0CTBJ2%2BXWp%2BbdMqCTEImU9xBYUFqzJ9ku6QlcRMTUk3htJNP8%2BPDsz%2F2%2FvaZxjySc8S52Wudy7%2FiOVpgO7BhUIsF2WEeZM4NcBxHbEL9SSRz7JrB58dFcNLBfQWRXE1vYNU0j4MfdSIbV8CEDnMupjNgIxUVZza8Z8wkB9eaalcyZlrcvKB%2FQyHzzfd8D8ZaBv65EqCeLTZLbjVbheBes1sI5l8zxSpi2S38Z6ChM08QQUvsh8W7NP%2BISF6cc%2FUKsQq7P6h8ycEvGFjzN%2Fh%2Fc4HwhoMoRfTOChAYO7Oxv494SxoxUzc8A2mhwS7gDZcRe%2FTx6pwmEvsQFRmDkwOZGE1cWFgRVAuU1LoRAPsG7xHsit9yyAyJJ7dCySSGeBY1YnnLzSNpFigxEQGHkkBHgl25SnUk